===Proper noun===
'''Common Slavonic'''

# The proto-language from which [[Old Church Slavonic]] and all the other Slavic languages later emerged. It was spoken before the 7th century.

===Synonyms===
*[[Old Slavonic]]
*[[proto-Slavic]]

